Package sokoban

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Avatar
    Class, wich is responsible for player avatar
    Background
    This class creates and paint the background of the level
    Chest
    This class creates and paints moveable chests which will be pushed by the player
    Counter
    This class controls time of the level
    CurrentLevel
    Abstract class, which chooses config file to load and saves properties of specific level
    DrawMap
    Class used to draw game objects and map.
    Endpoint
    This class creates and paints unmoveable endpoints.
    FinishGame
    Class, which object is created when game is finished.
    Game
    This is the class that controls the game layout.
    GameControler
    Used to transfer data between game objects
    GameObject
    Abstract class of the graphical components of the game
    Leader
    Class defining single leader on leaderboard.
    Leaderboard
    Reads leaders from file and displays on the screen.
    LevelLabel
    Informs the player which level he is taking
    LevelMap
    Class which deals with current level map.
    Lives
    This class shows how many lives a player has.
    MainMenu
    This the class of the main menu, also it is starting class,which have main function.
    Manual
    Displays tips how to play the game.
    MenuControler
    Controls main menu.
    OptionPane
    This is class, which takes care of options of the game
    Points
    This class calculates and shows points
    Rules
    Displays rules of the game.
    Sokoban
    Acts as a "launcher".
    Wall
    This class draws walls - unmoveable obstacles in the game
